39:24.700 --> 39:24.820
Right.

39:24.960 --> 39:28.200
They're both spherical fruits that grow on trees and contain vitamin C.

39:28.780 --> 39:30.620
In an embedding space, they are neighbors.

39:31.440 --> 39:35.480
